[待翻译] The spawn rate for lanterns in the main shaft.

[待翻译] The number of "pieces" (e.g. straight, turn, etc) in a single small shaft.
[待翻译] This determines the overall size of small shafts.

[待翻译] The spawn rate for smaller tunnels that generate along the main shaft.

[待翻译] Workstation Spawn Rate
[待翻译] The spawn rate for workstation side rooms along the main shaft.
